x plus a squared plus b,

00:00:42.148 --> 00:00:45.936
and we'll see if we can write
the left-hand in this form

00:00:45.936 --> 00:00:47.640
that we can actually solve it

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:49.072
in a pretty straightforward way.

00:00:49.072 --> 00:00:50.744
So let's see if we could do that.

00:00:50.744 --> 00:00:52.736
Well let's just remind ourselves

