00:01:33.416 --> 00:01:34.958
So I just rewrote this equation,

00:01:34.958 --> 00:01:36.629
but I gave myself some space

00:01:36.629 --> 00:01:38.271
so I can add or subtract some things

00:01:38.271 --> 00:01:39.933
that might make it a little bit easier

00:01:39.933 --> 00:01:41.468
to get into this form.

